- 'Non-compliant' means these dependencies do not meet the required security standards;
- 'Recently turned non-compliant' indicates that the compliance status was updated within the last 30 days.

- 'Blossoms' refer to the most highly rated dependencies;
- 'Admiration and attention' refer to high average ratings and a large number of reviews;
- 'Shining brightly' indicates the top-ranked dependencies in each project.

sql:
SELECT DISTINCT d.name
FROM dependencies d
JOIN dependency_vulnerabilities dv ON d.dependency_id = dv.dependency_id;

